  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595967645397-IN9BSVUDH3W5YFH40ZCS/12a-Quote%2Bby%2BBeau%2BTaplin%2B_%2BScripted%2Bby%2BAmy%2BTangerine.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<figcaption>\n<p>Found <a href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/173529391870486708/\">this quote on Pinterest</a> and it was just too good to not script out. After some googling, I discovered it was by <a href=\"http://www.beautaplin.com/\">Beau Taplin</a>. I found myself lost in reading more of his work, but since I have to get to work myself, I am saving it for later when I have more time to dive in. Have a wonderful, unstoppable week, friends!</p><p>I'm using <a href=\"http://goo.gl/zMVzgS\">this watercolor set from Michaels</a> and a waterbrush <a href=\"http://goo.gl/eDsF0u\">that I love by Tim Holtz/Ranger</a>. If you have a favorite quote – silly, snarky or simple in its’ wisdom, please share in the comments!</p>\n</figcaption>\n</figure>"
